text: Elias Allenspach (born 14 May 2001) is a Swiss snowboarder who competed in the men's halfpipe at the 2018 Winter Olympics, but did not qualify for the medal round. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male snowboarders Category:Olympic snowboarders of Switzerland Category:Snowboarders at the 2018 Winter Olympics
title: Elias Allenspach
